{"tid":348863,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★蘋果 2017Q3 大中華銷售急跌！Tim Cook：香港「陀衰家」！","createTime":"2017-08-06T05:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T11:30:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"653e7caf2b4288ce1ffb9da2e73b2a7b298edea3","tid":348863,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"蘋果今晨公開 2017Q3 業績，銷售額和盈利同比平穩增長，但是唯獨大中華區的銷售仍然比上一年急跌，最近 Tim Cook 在 CNBC 的訪問將大中華區銷售不振責任全推給香港身上。<br />\n<br />\nTim Cook 在 CNBC 的訪問之中，再次針對香港銷售不振振達不滿，直指香港「陀衰」大中華區銷售，在回答有關大中華銷售急跌的問題的時候，Tim Cook 提及蘋果在中國銷售同比上升了 5%，台灣銷售上升了 20%，但卻指因為香港銷售急跌，拖累大中華區整體下跌，但他沒有提供任何有關香港銷售的數字證明他的講法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/08/02/tim-cook-blames-apple-hong-kong-sales-weak/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2Ftim-cook-blames-apple-hong-kong-sales-weak%2F&d=RXwih5i%2FRi3UFcgrGh8mwROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=546b7060\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/08/02/tim-cook-blames-apple-hong-kong-sales-weak/</a>"},{"pid":"d3065b66e606c0eb767086862eee912744c5fc80","tid":348863,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300724675bccf4ff7d682d3707ef22d53fd2b128","tid":348863,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:53:12.000Z","msg":"等睇冇ifans理你"},{"pid":"4cd4f56e09b9117bd9251b1851ee6c4bce93179d","tid":348863,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇冇ifans理你</blockquote><br />\n游b理，已經足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\